					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Well, 16x16 is used because 1 tile is SMALL. And, then, most tiles you won't be able to put because of color differences, and it'll take 4x more memory to do it probably, because it's 4x more tiles. I think 16x16 tiles should be used pretty much always, unless you use MMC5 and can get single colored tiles. But even then it may be a waste. It'd certainly be waste of a mapper.</div>

