					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">In games that use 16x16 pixel blocks, or 2x2 tiles, you can put ANY block there. But if you do a 1 tile per byte way, you won't be able to put pretty much any type of tile except one of the same colors, making it difficult to have an advantage at all of not using 2x2 tiles.</div>

